---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Testimonials from '../components/Testimonials.astro';
---

<Layout title="Alpha Gamma Omega | UC Berkeley">
	<main>
		<Header />
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What is AGO?</h2>
					<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
						Alpha Gamma Omega is the largest college social fraternity in the world, with over 250,000 living members spanning across 17,000 active graduates and nearly 700 chapters and colonies. Founded on Christian principles, AGO has been developing men of character and fostering lifelong brotherhood since its establishment. Our fraternity maintains a strong presence across college campuses nationwide, with our International headquarters located in Charlottesville, Virginia.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Beta Chapter</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
							The Alpha Gamma Omega chapter at UC Berkeley is called the Beta Chapter. We are the only Christ-centered fraternity at UC Berkeley and are recognized by the IFC. We are also actively involved in the Greek system, in local churches, and in the Cal community. Many of the active members of the fraternity live at the house, which is 3 blocks from campus. Non-members also live at the house. As Christians, and as a Christ-centered fraternity, we believe that we are called by God to love and serve those around us.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="relative h-[400px]">
						<img 
							src="/ago/pensieve.jpg" 
							alt="Beta Chapter Image" 
							class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Testimonials />
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
					<div class="relative h-[400px]">
						<img 
							src="/ago/pismo.jpg" 
							alt="Housing Image" 
							class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
						/>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Want to live at the house?</h2>
						<span class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
							If you are a male college student looking for housing, Alpha Gamma Omega might be the place for you! Included in rent is all utilities, internet, laundry, and a friendly community! <a href="/housing" class="ml-1 font-semibold text-purple-600">Learn more &rarr;</a>
						</span>
						
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Interested in joining?</h2>
						<p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
							We are a Christian-centric organization, with each chapter having its own schedule of events and activities. Choosing Alpha Gamma Omega is your first step to brotherhood in a life-changing Christian fraternity that will make an impact in your life. <a href="/rush" class="ml-1 font-semibold text-purple-600">Rush &rarr;</a>
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="relative h-[400px]">
						<img 
							src="/ago/pismo.jpg" 
							alt="Rush Group Photo" 
							class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-lg"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-green-500 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-12 text-center">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">Connect With Us</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed mb-8">
					Stay connected with us through our social media channels or reach out for more information.
				</p>
				<div class="flex justify-center space-x-6 mb-8">
					<a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-purple-500">
						<img src="/ago/instagram-color.svg" alt="Instagram" class="h-10 w-10">
					</a>
					<a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-purple-500">
						<img src="/ago/x-color.svg" alt="Twitter" class="h-10 w-10">
					</a>
					<a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-purple-500">
						<img src="/ago/facebook-color.svg" alt="Facebook" class="h-10 w-10">
					</a>
					<a href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-purple-500">
						<img src="/ago/youtube-color.svg" alt="YouTube" class="h-10 w-10">
					</a>
					<a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="hover:text-purple-500">
						<img src="/ago/linkedin-color.svg" alt="LinkedIn" class="h-10 w-10">
					</a>
				</div>
				<div class="flex justify-center items-center space-x-6">
					<a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-purple-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-purple-500 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
						Contact Us
					</a>
					<a href="/about" class="text-lg font-semibold text-white hover:text-gray-100 transition duration-150 ease-in-out">
						Learn More &rarr;
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>